95% of presentations are boring. Everybody use PowerPoint few people know how to use it.

This post is number 3 to introduce you a very good serie of slides written [Eduardo S. de la Fuente](http://www.slideshare.net/eduardo.delafuente) .

If you do presentations, you should read this carefully.

If you missed previous posts, they are [here](http://laurentmaumet.com/english/the-art-of-presentation-1/), and  [here](http://laurentmaumet.com/english/the-art-of-presentation-2-we-need-to-improve-our-presentations/).

